window.bookSummaryJSON = "Ben, Chloe, Mark, and the others are off on another adventure, one in which they stumble across another war out in the depths of space.<br><br>But, this time, there are no obvious good aliens and bad aliens, and things are not going their way.<br><br>One encounter somehow morphs into a Cozy Alien Murder Mystery.<br><br>Another involves a race composed of potentially poisonous toxic material that can shape shift.<br><br>Then, they encounter even more aliens, and nothing is what it seems. The clues are there, but one wrong step, and there will be more dead aliens and possibly dead humans."; 
